pullRequest.body:
Generalize `ContinuousLinearMap.compSL` to topological vector spaces.

---

- [ ] depends on: #15217 

This PR is not polished yet, but the main statement is there.
@ADedecker This answers a question I asked you on Zulip a few months ago.
